metadata.name: Bad Billy Goats #1
metadata.description: Bad Billy Goats is a collection of 8888 of the Baddest Goats around. 1888 of these goat will be Minted on Ethereum and will receive weekly rewards and an NFT Airdrop. Our utilities include Lottery, Staking, Games, Events, and Royalties going back to the holders. Our first collection on the Cronos Network Sold Out immediately and we will bring that same momentum to ETH. The other 7000 pieces of our collection will be Minted on the Cronos Network in April, this is also when we will airdrop to our ETH Goat holders. The Creator and Artist Matthew von Prisk fully Doxxed and always available through Discord or Twitter!
